<h2 class="bold font-l">Calhorns Backstory</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
&quot;It's not her fault. She's programmed with the most tragic backstory ever.&quot; Kohutt explains the reason behind Calhorn's personality, her fiance was killed during her wedding day because she didn't run a perimeter check. </p>
</div>
